From 421d678da7c24439aeb23370723181dc6e6ed6ac Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: yangsonglin13 <yangsonglin566@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 23:11:41 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] fix(rfork): support quantized and draft transfers

Support RFork transfer for quantized models, keep draft model loads on the RFork path during fallback, and sync tensor shape metadata from seed services before transferring weights.

Keep receiver transfer shape metadata in sync after local tensors are reshaped, and make remote transfer-info errors return the expected tuple shape.

Signed-off-by: yangsonglin13 <yangsonglin566@gmail.com>
